The paper focuses on using deep reinforcement learning for controlling robotic arms, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning techniques such as deep learning (cs.LG) and reinforcement learning (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of computer vision (cs.CV) for preprocessing information before feeding it to the reinforcement learning algorithm. Finally, the paper discusses the use of control systems (cs.SY) to evaluate the effectiveness of the proposed approach.
